OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist, fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fclears inland, while mist and low
OL,7,Fcloud is likely to linger along the
OL,8,Fcoast. Becoming warm inland with sunny
OL,9,Fspells, the sunshine often hazy, but
OL,10,Fremaining cool near the coast with an
OL,11,Fonshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely clear initially then
OL,14,Fmist and low cloud is expected to
OL,15,Fextend inland from the coast. Chance
OL,16,Fof a slight frost, and patchy fog, for
OL,17,Fany places that remain clear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
